{
  "sourceLanguage":"en",
  "strings":{
    "About Sasu":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Sasuについて"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"关于 Sasu"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"關於 Sasu"}}}},
    "Accept Screen Recording":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"画面収録を許可"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"允许屏幕录制"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"允許螢幕錄製"}}}},
    "Access":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"アクセス"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"访问方式"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"存取方式"}}}},
    "Accessibility permission granted":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"アクセシビリティの許可済み"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"已授予辅助功能权限"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"已授予輔助使用權限"}}}},
    "Accessibility permission required":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"アクセシビリティの許可が必要です"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"需要辅助功能权限"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"需要輔助使用權限"}}}},
    "After changing Screen Recording permission, macOS usually requires quitting and reopening Sasu before capture works.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"画面収録の許可を変更した後は、通常、Sasuを終了して再度開くまでキャプチャを使用できません。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"更改屏幕录制权限后，通常需要退出并重新打开 Sasu，捕捉功能才能正常使用。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"更改螢幕錄製權限後，通常需要結束並重新開啟 Sasu，擷取功能才能正常使用。"}}}},
    "After enabling Accessibility for Sasu, macOS usually requires quitting and reopening Sasu before Translate & Replace works.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Sasuのアクセシビリティを有効にした後は、通常、Sasuを終了して再度開くまで「翻訳して置換」を使用できません。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"为 Sasu 启用辅助功能后，通常需要退出并重新打开 Sasu，“翻译并替换”才能正常使用。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"為 Sasu 啟用輔助使用後，通常需要結束並重新開啟 Sasu，「翻譯並取代」才能正常使用。"}}}},
    "AI":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"AI"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"AI"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"AI"}}}},
    "AI Model":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"AIモデル"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"AI 模型"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"AI 模型"}}}},
    "Answer copied to clipboard.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答をクリップボードにコピーしました。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答已复制到剪贴板。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答已複製到剪貼簿。"}}}},
    "Answer ready.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答の準備ができました。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答已就绪。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答已就緒。"}}}},
    "Answering…":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答中…"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正在回答…"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正在回答…"}}}},
    "API key saved in Keychain":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"APIキーはキーチェーンに保存されています"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"API 密钥已存储在钥匙串中"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"API 金鑰已儲存在鑰匙圈中"}}}},
    "Appearance":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"外観"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"外观"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"外觀"}}}},
    "Ask about this screenshot...":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"このスクリーンショットについて質問..."}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"询问有关此截屏的问题..."}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"詢問有關此截圖的問題..."}}}},
    "Asking OpenAI…":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"OpenAIに問い合わせ中…"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正在询问 OpenAI…"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正在詢問 OpenAI…"}}}},
    "Auto-hides after 5 seconds.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"5秒後に自動的に非表示になります。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"5 秒后自动隐藏。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"5 秒後自動隱藏。"}}}},
    "Automatically include full Safari page content":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Safariページ全体の内容を自動的に含める"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"自动包含完整的 Safari 页面内容"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"自動包含完整的 Safari 頁面內容"}}}},
    "Best (GPT-5.6 High Fast)":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"最高（GPT-5.6 High Fast）"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"最佳（GPT-5.6 High Fast）"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"最佳（GPT-5.6 High Fast）"}}}},
    "Better (GPT-5.6 Medium Fast)":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"高品質（GPT-5.6 Medium Fast）"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"更佳（GPT-5.6 Medium Fast）"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"更佳（GPT-5.6 Medium Fast）"}}}},
    "Capture":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"キャプチャ"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"捕捉"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"擷取"}}}},
    "Capture & Ask":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"キャプチャして質問"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"捕捉并提问"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"擷取並提問"}}}},
    "Capture a screenshot first...":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"先にスクリーンショットを撮影してください..."}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"请先捕捉截屏..."}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"請先擷取截圖..."}}}},
    "Capture Screen":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"画面をキャプチャ"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"捕捉屏幕"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"擷取螢幕"}}}},
    "Capture stopped.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"キャプチャを停止しました。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"捕捉已停止。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"擷取已停止。"}}}},
    "Capturing screen...":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"画面をキャプチャ中..."}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正在捕捉屏幕..."}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正在擷取螢幕..."}}}},
    "Check for Updates…":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"アップデートを確認…"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"检查更新…"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"檢查更新…"}}}},
    "Choose at least one modifier for the Capture & Ask hotkey.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"「キャプチャして質問」のホットキーには修飾キーを1つ以上選択してください。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"请为“捕捉并提问”快捷键至少选择一个修饰键。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"請為「擷取並提問」快速鍵至少選擇一個變更鍵。"}}}},
    "Choose at least one modifier for the global hotkey.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"グローバルホットキーには修飾キーを1つ以上選択してください。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"请为全局快捷键至少选择一个修饰键。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"請為全域快速鍵至少選擇一個變更鍵。"}}}},
    "Choose at least one modifier for the Translate & Replace hotkey.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"「翻訳して置換」のホットキーには修飾キーを1つ以上選択してください。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"请为“翻译并替换”快捷键至少选择一个修饰键。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"請為「翻譯並取代」快速鍵至少選擇一個變更鍵。"}}}},
    "Choose at least one modifier for the Translate Selection hotkey.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"「選択範囲を翻訳」のホットキーには修飾キーを1つ以上選択してください。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"请为“翻译所选内容”快捷键至少选择一个修饰键。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"請為「翻譯所選內容」快速鍵至少選擇一個變更鍵。"}}}},
    "Choose the language you translate from":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"翻訳元の言語を選択"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"选择翻译源语言"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"選擇翻譯來源語言"}}}},
    "Clear":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"消去"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"清除"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"清除"}}}},
    "Clear Invite Access":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"招待アクセスを消去"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"清除邀请访问权限"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"清除邀請存取權"}}}},
    "Clear Key":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"キーを消去"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"清除密钥"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"清除金鑰"}}}},
    "Click `Sasuを始める` to start using Sasu.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"「Sasuを始める」をクリックしてSasuの使用を開始します。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"点击“Sasuを始める”即可开始使用 Sasu。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按一下「Sasuを始める」即可開始使用 Sasu。"}}}},
    "Click Sasuを始める in the example to enable Screen Recording first.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"まず例の「Sasuを始める」をクリックして画面収録を有効にしてください。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"请先点击示例中的“Sasuを始める”以启用屏幕录制。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"請先按一下範例中的「Sasuを始める」以啟用螢幕錄製。"}}}},
    "Click this green button to get started.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"この緑色のボタンをクリックして始めます。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"点击此绿色按钮即可开始。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按一下這個綠色按鈕即可開始。"}}}},
    "Command":{"comment":"A macOS keyboard modifier key.","localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Command"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Command"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Command"}}}},
    "Control":{"comment":"A macOS keyboard modifier key.","localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Control"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Control"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Control"}}}},
    "Copy Answer":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"回答をコピー"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"复制回答"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"複製回答"}}}},
    "Copy Link":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"リンクをコピー"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"复制链接"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"複製連結"}}}},
    "Could not create report: %@":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"レポートを作成できませんでした：%@"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"无法创建报告：%@"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"無法建立報告：%@"}}}},
    "Could not open Mail. The report file was shown in Finder.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"メールを開けませんでした。レポートファイルをFinderに表示しました。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"无法打开“邮件”。报告文件已显示在“访达”中。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"無法開啟「郵件」。報告檔案已顯示於 Finder。"}}}},
    "Could not open screenshot preview.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"スクリーンショットのプレビューを開けませんでした。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"无法打开截屏预览。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"無法開啟截圖預覽。"}}}},
    "Current page":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"現在のページ"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"当前页面"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"目前頁面"}}}},
    "Current: %@":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"現在：%@"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"当前：%@"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"目前：%@"}}}},
    "Decrease Text Size":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"文字を小さく"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"减小文本大小"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"縮小文字"}}}},
    "Do Not Include":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"含めない"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"不包含"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"不包含"}}}},
    "Don’t Ask Again":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"今後確認しない"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"不再询问"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"不再詢問"}}}},
    "Double-click to open screenshot":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"ダブルクリックしてスクリーンショットを開く"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"双击打开截屏"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按兩下以開啟截圖"}}}},
    "Enable for Safari":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Safariで有効にする"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"为 Safari 启用"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"為 Safari 啟用"}}}},
    "Enable Translate & Replace?":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"「翻訳して置換」を有効にしますか？"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"启用“翻译并替换”？"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"啟用「翻譯並取代」？"}}}},
    "English":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"英語"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"英语"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"英文"}}}},
    "Error":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"エラー"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"错误"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"錯誤"}}}},
    "Follow-up":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"追加の質問"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"后续问题"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"後續問題"}}}},
    "Full Safari page included":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Safariページ全体を含めました"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"已包含完整的 Safari 页面"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"已包含完整的 Safari 頁面"}}}},
    "General":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"一般"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"通用"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"一般"}}}},
    "Have questions? Contact me (the developer).":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"ご質問は開発者までお問い合わせください。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"有疑问？请联系我（开发者）。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"有疑問？請聯絡我（開發者）。"}}}},
    "Have questions about privacy?":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"プライバシーについてご質問がありますか？"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"对隐私有疑问？"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"對隱私有疑問？"}}}},
    "Hide":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"隠す"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"隐藏"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"隱藏"}}}},
    "Hide guidance":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"案内を隠す"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"隐藏指引"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"隱藏指引"}}}},
    "Hotkeys":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"ホットキー"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"快捷键"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"快速鍵"}}}},
    "Include":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"含める"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"包含"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"包含"}}}},
    "Include Full Safari Page?":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Safariページ全体を含めますか？"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"包含完整的 Safari 页面？"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"包含完整的 Safari 頁面？"}}}},
    "Increase Text Size":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"文字を大きく"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"增大文本大小"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"放大文字"}}}},
    "Invite access":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"招待アクセス"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"邀请访问"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"邀請存取"}}}},
    "Invite access saved in Keychain":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"招待アクセスはキーチェーンに保存されています"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"邀请访问权限已存储在钥匙串中"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"邀請存取權已儲存在鑰匙圈中"}}}},
    "Japanese":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"日本語"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"日语"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"日文"}}}},
    "Key":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"キー"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按键"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按鍵"}}}},
    "Key %lld":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"キー %lld"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按键 %lld"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"按鍵 %lld"}}}},
    "Made in Japan":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"日本製"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"日本制造"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"日本製造"}}}},
    "My OpenAI API key":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"自分のOpenAI APIキー"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"我的 OpenAI API 密钥"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"我的 OpenAI API 金鑰"}}}},
    "No API key saved":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"APIキーは保存されていません"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"未存储 API 密钥"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"未儲存 API 金鑰"}}}},
    "No invite access saved":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"招待アクセスは保存されていません"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"未存储邀请访问权限"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"未儲存邀請存取權"}}}},
    "Not Now":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"今はしない"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"暂不"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"稍後"}}}},
    "Not Yet":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"後で"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"暂不"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"稍後"}}}},
    "On-screen guidance for macOS":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"macOSの画面上で操作を案内"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"macOS 屏幕操作指引"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"macOS 螢幕操作指引"}}}},
    "On your command, Sasu will capture your screen, then wait for your question before sending anything.":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"指示するとSasuが画面をキャプチャし、質問を入力するまで何も送信せずに待機します。"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"收到您的指令后，Sasu 会捕捉屏幕，并在发送任何内容之前等待您输入问题。"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"收到您的指令後，Sasu 會擷取螢幕，並在傳送任何內容之前等待您輸入問題。"}}}},
    "Open Accessibility Settings":{"localizations":{"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"アクセシビリティ設定を開く"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"打开辅助功能设置"}},"zh-Hant":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"開啟輔助使用設定"}}}},
